Douglas Cox took over from him followed by David Cox, Walter's sons.
David and his wife, Kathleen, retired 16 years ago and now Samantha, their daughter, and her husband John, run the shop.
Over the years the shop has sold many different products including paint, prams, clothes and shoes.
